# Use Cases Design as Demo for presentation
Author: Roy Yang
Date: Thu Mar 19 09:43:20 CST 2015
The most simplest use cases are designed, for the presentation use. NOTICE that this does NOT equal to a well-designed or a fully-covered test.

### Use Cases

#### Visit as an Anonymous User (匿名用户)
##### Check activities
###### Check activities by place index
    1. 首页点击”地点“
    2. 在索引列表中选择某一层级的地理位置 
    3. 从展现的活动列表当中选择任意一个活动查看
###### Check activities recommended on the activity page
    1. 首页点击”活动“
    2. 从展现的活动列表当中选择任意一个活动查看

##### Check places by place index
    1. 首页点击”地点“
    2. 在索引列表中选择某一层级的地理位置
    3. 从展现的地点列表当中选择任意一个地点进行查看

