##### Register to become a member
    1. 首页点击“注册”
    2. 按照指引填写相应的个人信息
    3. 等待确认邮件
    4. 确认注册
##### Complete personal infos
    1. 进入个人信息页面
    2. 点击“完善个人资料”
    3. 按照指引填写相应的个人信息
    3. 等待确认（站内信）


#### Visit as a Registered User (注册用户)
    A REGISTERED User should be able to do all activities available for an ANONYMOUS User, firstly.
##### Get participated in an activity
    （选择活动后）
    4. 点击“参与活动”

##### Make personal posts
    （在相应的页面，填写足够的信息后，点击上传/发布）
###### Post a personal blog
###### Create a album
###### Post a photo

##### Do Comments
    （在相应的页面，填写评论内容，发布评论）
###### Comment on an activity
###### Comment on others blogs
###### Comment on others photos

##### Send messages to another user
    1. 选择相应的用户
    2. 点击发送私信
    3. 确认发送
##### Send messages to another user<2>
    1. 点击新建私信
    2. 选择相应的用户
    3. 确认发送


#### Visit as a High-Priviledge User (高级用户如认证后用户等)
    A HIGH-PREVILEDGED User should be able to do all activities available for a REGISTERED User, firstly.
##### Create an activity
    1. 点击“创建活动”
    2. 按照指引填写相应的活动详细信息
    3. 发布活动

